All Classes

Class Description
CollectionSchema
A CollectionSchema represents the schema of a non-relational collection.
CollectionSchema.InvalidAttributeIndexException
An InvalidAttributeIndexException is thrown if an invalid attribute index is given to a CollectionSchema.
CollectionSchemaTestAdvanced
This program tests the CollectionSchema class.
CollectionSchemaTestBasic
This program tests the CollectionSchema class.
DataObject
A DataObject represents an entity using a number of attributes organized possibly in a hierarchical fashion.
DataObjectTestAdvanced
This program tests the DataObject class.
DataObjectTestBasic
This program tests the DataObject class.
RelationSchema
A RelationSchema represents the schema of a relation.
RelationSchema.InvalidAttributeIndexException
An InvalidAttributeIndexException is thrown if an invalid attribute index is given to a RelationSchema.
RelationSchema.InvalidRelationSchemaDefinitionException
An InvalidRelationSchemaDefinition is thrown if a RelationSchema is defined inappropriately.
RelationSchemaTest
This program tests the RelationSchema class.
Tuple
A Tuple represents a record in a relation containing a number of attributes.
Tuple.TypeException
A TypeException is thrown when an object is not an instance of an appropriate type.
TupleTest
This program tests the Tuple class.
TupleTest.WritingTask
A WritingTask represents a task that can possibly write data to an ObjectOutputStream.
